    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Average Height:</strong> 5´ 6˝–6´ 2˝</p><p><strong>Average Weight:</strong> 140–230 lb.</p><p><strong>Ability Score:</strong></p><ul><li>+2 Intelligence</li><li>+2 Charisma</li></ul><p><strong>Size: </strong>Medium</p><p><strong>Base Speed:</strong> 6 squares</p><p><strong>Vision:</strong> Low-light</p><p><strong>Languages:</strong></p><ul><li>Common</li><li>choice of one other</li></ul><p><strong>Skill </strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary)\"><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">Bonuses:</strong></span></p><ul><li>+2 Bluff</li><li>+2 Stealth</li></ul><p><strong>Bloodhunt: </strong>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.YVyfBmcrLW74Aj6t]{You gain a +1 racial bonus to attack rolls against bloodied foes.}</p><p><strong>Fire </strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary)\"><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">Resistance:</strong> </span>You have resist fire 5 + one-half your level.</p><p><strong>Infernal Wrath: </strong>Gain the @UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.RLXIMXEIueFwMMAE]{Infernal Wrath} as an encounter power.</p>",
